title: Amy’s Doggie Lama Works Wonders + Grocery Store Joe Stops By
itunes:title: Amy’s Doggie Lama Works Wonders + Grocery Store Joe Stops By
description:
Amy hires a ‘doggie lama’ to help train the rescue dog she recently adopted. Bobby talks with Grocery Store Joe about being the ‘non-dancers’ on Dancing With The Stars. Also, Lunchbox hits the streets to get opinions on if Bobby can win the mirrorball trophy.
